{"tid":220464,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去旅行出發之前你地會唔會搵定交通資料？","createTime":"2017-04-28T03:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T13:31:53.000Z","uid":16418,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"968af911685dd94aaf35a7d579176c171beee146","tid":220464,"uid":16418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"想問各位巴絲自由行嘅話出發之前會唔會搵定當地嘅交通資料？<br />\n我發覺好多嚟香港嘅遊客（尤其是大陸人）落咗機先喺機場問人點搭車去酒店 而之前完全冇做過research <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲更加過分 連自己住嗰間酒店個名都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家大家去旅行"},{"pid":"724344537a8317021a539a61886a207a41292851","tid":220464,"uid":16418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問各位巴絲自由行嘅話出發之前會唔會搵定當地嘅交通資料？<br />\n我發覺好多嚟香港嘅遊客（尤其是大陸人）落咗機先喺機場問人點搭車去酒店 而之前完全冇做過research <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲更加過分 連自己住嗰間酒店個名都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家大家去旅行<span style=\"color: red;\">係會倚賴當地人定係出發之前google</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"b15fe370aa1ac8e54539bba2d7552c936bc51bb4","tid":220464,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:19:53.000Z","msg":"會搵 起碼知個大概"},{"pid":"f7f67e771a5f4fc462f7434c8e634c27a2522bc3","tid":220464,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"會，仲會睇埋google map酒店附近街景，方便落車行去果陣大概知係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208e0172c11e5bc4fa6bdf2dc1c27431009384a8","tid":220464,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"肯定會<br />\n費時去到企度慢慢搵<br />\n仲要未必即時上到網<br />\n所以至少搵定落機之後第一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e9ac3f462cbd0a6b4f09fe3ce095fe0265dd53","tid":220464,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"一定會啦...問人不如問GOOGLE"},{"pid":"80aca3276b3c511a4ebcf86c18909a4d99f4b833","tid":220464,"uid":16418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"仲以為依家興問人多過問google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到啲人喺度問問問但自己完全冇搵過料真係會躁底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46badd7358471c8c7c2f368944547721d879a2f","tid":220464,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:32:02.000Z","msg":"會，去開冷門地方，唔做唔得。"},{"pid":"544ed4555529bd2f2a83724a09816dc15d10b029","tid":220464,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"我自己係prepare 晒所有會去既地方電話, 因為有電話number 係日本, 開map 係可以直接show 你現時地方點去電話number 既地點.<br />\n<br />\n所有既意思係所有會去既景點, 午餐晚餐地點, 所有入住酒店地點, 每個地點去下一個地點既travel time, 玩咁多日就打晒落notepad."},{"pid":"1c9297a61f288ec8a0db43ce3a693b58555dca9f","tid":220464,"uid":16418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己係prepare 晒所有會去既地方電話, 因為有電話number 係日本, 開map 係可以直接show 你現時地方點去電話number 既地點.<br />\n<br />\n所有既意思係所有會去既景點, 午餐晚餐地點, 所有入住酒店地點, 每個地點去下一個地點既travel time, 玩咁多日就打晒落notepad.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果個個遊客好似你咁盡返自己嘅責任就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7aa2d2eeeb0d57563525f7a3f2069e2fda8419","tid":220464,"uid":292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"除非預左的士/私家車出入,唔係都會搵左先"},{"pid":"2ea83e78a6d00becc11de6efcc648a509818ae84","tid":220464,"uid":2990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"靠你搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e219ee1d717fee40ce7fded8423e1963c9741d15","tid":220464,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"試過去和歌山<br />\n朝早食早餐果陣同女朋友傾緊琴日去黑潮市場既野<br />\n<br />\n之後輪住3枱香港人黎問我應該點去<br />\n全部都有禮貌+自己睇過下書, 不過話D書寫到唔清唔楚<br />\n而且佢地都上左年紀 唔係18 22<br />\n所以我全部都有答<br />\n<br />\n上左年紀就無得講, 因為佢地唔太識電腦 主要睇書<br />\n書又真係好難講點去"},{"pid":"f775bdb7f620bc8caa9cae3d64abd2d49116b239","tid":220464,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"有上網 基本上一個Google Map 就解決"},{"pid":"62c31f23f05292b6c81fbf8c448fe538fb454bef","tid":220464,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"a833475416a850a20f85b948ea11a7a123c188df","tid":220464,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"應該會"},{"pid":"22babfda68664add6c46487d7e25195d4535af51","tid":220464,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"唔搵到時冇上網就食得屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3042c9bbdf005d8c7112add25f93df56874881","tid":220464,"uid":47654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"機場酒店交通最基本<br />\n其他偏遠地方都會搵埋<br />\n但如果係市內交通就到時先搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf8626b31d88d0337591d80273cec2a60d218e9","tid":220464,"uid":56636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人會去之前用google map 行一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1882e1c989382fa8d9692245ddbe9a651a2fc7de","tid":220464,"uid":13199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"我會。來回機場交通會搵好路線同班次+後備方案。<br />\n偏遠景點都會睇定，鬧市區內就大慨知有咩車就算，到時再google map。"},{"pid":"97d55a7bc7c7a374fd92da5baedc7365caa14f29","tid":220464,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"睇埋車站邊個出口出<br />\nGoogle map行一次先"},{"pid":"c531c99df6b8c1c50ff45f5d45780fba150a3868","tid":220464,"uid":80586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"我自己會<br />\n聽過有d fd 話會唔prepare去旅行，去到問人睇地圖點都好，話覺得咁樣先係自由行，9行好free喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fefb7e1c16fd4f6330e35bb13fd01d2ac1eb983","tid":220464,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"一定會"},{"pid":"992c000b2479b4e5c6ed316bc0b63416ee058452","tid":220464,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"建議你同大陸人講坐的士<br />\n「打的吧！很快到！」<br />\n<br />\n振興香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee971a68da97fc77c9276aa7443f064f1308f73c","tid":220464,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人會去之前用google map 行一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打,呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}